@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}

@* About the application *@
<div class="container py-5">
    <h1 class="fw-bold">About Discipline Dashboard</h1>

    <p class="lead mt-3">
        Discipline Dashboard is a personal productivity app designed to help users build better habits,
        track goals, reflect through journaling, and stay consistent over time.
    </p>

    <p>
        The application was built with ASP.NET Core MVC, Entity Framework Core, Identity authentication,
        and a relational database. Each user has their own private account, meaning habits, goals,
        journal entries, and progress data are tied specifically to that user.
    </p>

    <p>
        The goal of this project is simple: create one place where users can organize their personal growth,
        daily discipline, and long-term progress.
    </p>
</div>